# Clash-FX cn-apps-direct-domains
# https://github.com/Clash-FX/cn-apps-direct-domains
#
# Curated DOMAIN-SUFFIX bypass rules for common Chinese apps.
# Domain-based companion to https://github.com/Clash-FX/cn-apps-direct
# (which uses PROCESS-NAME and only works under Enhanced Mode/TUN).
#
# This list works under BOTH Rule mode and Enhanced Mode, because it
# matches by domain instead of by process name.
#
# Format: mihomo / Clash classical rule-provider
# Inclusion policy: domestic-only domains. Apps with cross-border
# infrastructure (e.g. Lark's larksuite.com international tenant)
# are scoped to their mainland-only domains only.

